gif-forge (0.1.2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix single-frame wallpaper flashes in X11 recordings under a compositing
    desktop (x11grab racing the compositor repaint, seen on GNOME + NVIDIA):
    glitch frames are detected and repaired in every export path.
  * Fix uneven GIF frame timing from the editor export (100 ms frames came
    out as alternating 120/80 ms delays).

